                  "sourceNumber": 7,
                  "stage": "example",
                  "labelEn": "Example",
                  "labelZh": "例子",
                  "sourceLabel": "Example 2",
                  "textEn": "For instance, a teacher could include peer evaluation after a group activity and ask students to reflect on who listened well, who supported others, and how the team handled disagreement. That kind of reflection helps students see that teamwork is not just about the final result; it is also about the way people treat one another along the way.",
                  "textZh": "例如，老師可以在小組活動之後加入同儕評價，並請學生反思誰很願意聆聽、誰懂得支持別人，以及團隊是如何處理分歧的。這種反思能幫助學生明白，團隊合作不只是看最後的成果；同樣重要的，還有大家在過程中如何對待彼此。",
